<div class="eyebrow">CLINAMEN · Bureau of Imaginary Solutions</div>
<h1>The Model That Dreams Itself<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
<p class="byline">By <b>Gökhan Turhan</b> · <time datetime="2026-07-21">21 Jul 2026</time> · Numetal Labs</p>
    `,
